{"tid":1675584,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"我唔該選區議會個d同我認真些少","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T04:58:10.000Z","uid":327151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13f1aac887c593b70e55e981b9c7f254532d48ef","tid":1675584,"uid":327151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:57:44.000Z","msg":"小弟呢排放假 <br />\n閒時就落街食個靚lunch<br />\n我經常見到呢個鐘數我個區既工賊會淫賤聯派野<br />\n爭取d師奶嬸嬸既票 (佢地都應該算最搖擺不定既選民)<br />\n反觀打住本土既人我真係幾乎無見過<br />\n甚至熱狗我見得仲多<br />\n唔該你地認真d啦<br />\n我怕到時d淺黃叔叔姨姨<br />\n寧願投收過野既熱狗都唔投你呀<br />\n我本來諗住上個星期就出post<br />\n但每日一post block左我 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到今日發現我唔係唯一一個咁諗！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2432216943482110&amp;id=100000814848933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2432216943482110%26id%3D100000814848933&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtNyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=3a6d5933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2432216943482110&amp;id=100000814848933</a>"},{"pid":"0e4592a6db692d895a9a5a414e7475fc06b1411d","tid":1675584,"uid":19984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ctu4WC0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtu4WC0.jpg&h=0f6b4f14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRihxbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRihxbm.jpg&h=cb7e0abd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67ac1bbfbe9f23dc656a079630bbaf7ceaa61b3a","tid":1675584,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:35:03.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x